        * Bugfix: fix timeout bug in get_temperature(), requires i2cdevice>=0.0.7
        
        0.0.3
        -----
        
        * Bugfix: support 0 init value of MODE_CONFIG register
        
        0.0.2
        -----
        
        * Port to i2cdevice>=0.0.6 set/get API
        
        0.0.1
        -----
        
        * Initial Release
        
